ygData.messageBody:
Greetings Indigo Brother,

I am Jaade D'Vinn on Mith Maar, you are the highest level Dark Elf warrior I
have seen. I am level 17 and I am the highest on Mith Marr that I know off.

Nice to see there are others.

----- Original Message -----
From: Jason Coan <COANJ@...>
To: <warriors_eq@onelist.com>
Sent: Friday, May 14, 1999 8:45 AM
Subject: [warriors_eq] Hiyas


> From: "Jason Coan" <COANJ@...>
>
> Just signed up on the list, thought I'd take a minute to introduce myself
:)
>
> I'm Salr D'Taynkk, Dark Warrior of The Kith, Veeshan. I'm 24th, will be
25th tonight (reposte woohoo), Dark Elf warrior. I've been playing since
phase 2 and concider myself to be one of the better warriors of the land,
not due to my level or my equipment, but because I've been playing for a
while and know the role of a warrior in a party. I protect my healer with
my life, and will sacrifice myself to ensure the remainder of my party has a
few moments to escape....when necessary.
>
> As for weapons, my BBC is my primary weapon, but I also keep my 1h
slashing/dual wield skills up by using dual Barbed Leather Whips. I also
use archery, mainly for fetching monsters, but also use it when I get to
hurt to tank, I'll just back up and fire off arrows until I either get
healed or the critter is dead. Archery is a very underrated skill, I've
finally got my skill up to mid 80s and with the bow I have I can hit for up
to 12 damage, nothing major, but when you are hurt you can still dish out a
little damage.
>
> As for the rest of my equipment, I have a Blackend Iron Crown, Grotesque
mask, Spiked Collar, Rusty Spiked Pads, Barbed Arms, Blackend Bracers,
Blackend Gloves, Dwarven Tunic, Black Iron Girdle, Blackend legplates,
Blackend Boots, 2 ony earrings, 2 bands of flesh. Just a couple pieces
short of a full set of blackend, can't wait, should have those by the end of
the weekend :)
>
> Salr D'Taynkk
> Dark Warrior of The Kith
> Veeshan
>
>
